      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Slice the <strong>courgettes</strong> in half lengthways then scrape out the inner seeds using a teaspoon – these are your <strong>courgette boats</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>inner seeds</strong> roughly</p>",
