    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>courgette boats</strong> to a baking tray and fill them with the <strong>Greek cheese stuffing</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 12-15 min or until the courgette has softened and the Greek cheese stuffing is golden – this is your<strong> Greek cheese-stuffed courgette</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1669726915474-x200.jpg",
