    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the<strong> pestle & mortar</strong> and grind to a fine crumble – this is your <strong>pistachio dukkah</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
