    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped mint</strong> and <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> in a bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>mint yoghurt</strong></p><p>Once the rice is cooked, add the <strong>dried cranberries</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the pan and stir it all together until fully combined – this is your <strong>fruity rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
