      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fruity rice</strong> with the <strong>Greek cheese-stuffed courgette</strong> on top</p><p>Add a dollop of <strong>mint yoghurt</strong> to the side and sprinkle over the <strong>pistachio dukkah</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
